			<!--<p>EHRI-DR-19420822-IT_EN</p>
      <p>Report by <persName ref="ehri_raimondo_giustiniani">Giustiniani</persName> from <placeName
        ref="http://www.geonames.org/3186886/zagreb.html">Zagreb</placeName> to
        the Gabap, <date when="1942-08-22">22.8.1942</date>.</p>
      <p>Incoming telegram no. 5405 R</p>
      <p>Deciphered by: BF Cleartext - by courier</p>
      <p>Sender: R. Legation Zagreb</p>
      <p>Zagreb, 22.8.42/XX</p>
      <p>Rome, 24. Id.</p>
      <p>Assigned to: GABAP (U.Cr.)</p>
      <p>For perusal by: AG - AEM</p>-->
			<pb n="1" facs="EHRI-DR-19420822-IT_01.jpg"/>
			<p>Re: Treatment of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term></p>
			<p>As this Royal Legation reported in the telegram mentioned above, the transfer to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName> of the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jewish</term> survivors left in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/3202326/republic-of-croatia.html">Croatia</placeName> is currently under way. The transfer is carried
				out with special <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-940" type="subject">trains</term> provided by
					<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3202326/republic-of-croatia.html">Croatian</placeName> authorities, who, besides equipping
				the people who are leaving, are also required to pay the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948"
					type="subject">Government</term> of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1152" type="subject"
					>Reich</term> 30 Mark per person. (Initially the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1152"
					type="subject">Reich</term> had requested 500 Mark).</p>
			<pb n="2" facs="EHRI-DR-19420822-IT_02.jpg"/>
			<p>The said measures have led to a démarche – as the <persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000302"
					>Poglavnik</persName> himself has confirmed – by the Apostolic Delegate here, which brought no conclusive results. It seems,
				however, that the category formed by <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-373" type="subject">Aryans</term>
				joined in matrimony to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> will be left
				alone.</p>
			<p>The Minister of Germany here, in a conversation he had with the R. Minister about various issues, hinted at the advisability of
				starting to remove also the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> who have
				sought shelter in the 2nd zone occupied by <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3175395/italian-republic.html">Italian</placeName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1076" type="subject">troops</term> and asked how many there might be. He
				added that the larger <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">groups</term>, as far as he is
				was aware, ought to be <pb n="3" facs="EHRI-DR-19420822-IT_03.jpg"/> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3194828/mostar.html"
					>Mostar</placeName>, in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3201047/dubrovnik.html">Ragusa [Dubrovnik]</placeName> and in
					<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3202507/crikvenica.html">Cirquenizza [Crikvenica]</placeName>. Lastly, he hinted at an
				official step that the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">Government</term> of the
					<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1152" type="subject">Reich</term> is about to make in order to
				request that these <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>, like the others in
					<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3202326/republic-of-croatia.html">Croatia</placeName>, be also sent to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName>.</p>
			<p><persName ref="#ehri_dr_giustiniani_raimondo">Giustiniani</persName></p>
